abstract: Ben Ratlif reviews performance by Portuguese singer Ana Moura and Spanish singer Buika at Carnegie Hall.
lead_paragraph: The Spanish singer Buika followed the Portuguese singer Ms. Moura on Tuesday night in a double bill.

headline.main: Review: Ana Moura and Buika Negotiate Between Roots and Rules at Carnegie
headline.print_headline: Negotiating the Space Between Roots and Rules
